data.text:
Baby Shower Details for Poppy Montgomery – star of Without a Trace

I’ve been trying to follow Celebrity Pregnancies with due dates near or around my due date!

The adorable Poppy Montgomery, start of Without a Trace, is expecting on Dec 1st – just 8 days before me……. wonder who will have the baby first? Check out the below fun details on her baby shower – organized for her with the help of HUGGIES! Ah, those fringe benefits of being a celeb!

Poppy & her boyfriend, Actor Adam Kaufman, held the Baby Shower at their home on October 20th to celebrate the pending arrival of their soon-to-be son due December 1st! Guests included Poppy’s Without A Trace co-stars: Roselyn Sanchez, Enrique Murciano, Eric Close & Marianne Jean-Baptiste, as well as fellow-actress Elizabeth Berkley & her husband of four years, Actor Greg Lauren. The couple’s shower featured an animal show with a monkey, a lynx and an alligator as well as a cookie decorating station and a HUGGIES diaper fort! Guests snacked on mini-hamburgers, cupcakes, milk shakes and chocolate crackles as well as a delectable HUGGIES-themed cake!
